{
  "stem": "1918.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then-- and he said, just go ahead, and I'll do whatever needs to be done with it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And really, it was his opinion that mattered most to me, because he was the professional.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if he was satisfied, that was good enough for me to go on with.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept writing, to the point where one night I thought it was 3 o'clock in the morning, and I looked up and it was 7:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was still sitting at the typewriter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as he promised, he did whatever needed to be done with it to put it in publishable form.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And both our names appear on several books, because I went ahead and wrote a second book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first book was called It came out in 1978.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the second-- of And the second one was called And then there was a third one, the children's book, which has found great understanding with the children throughout the country.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's called And it has my family's picture on it, which is very painful to me, to go into a bookstore and see my family displayed all over.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to violate my sense of privacy in order to-- because I will only talk about what I know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I know is my family and what happened to them, so it's very painful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody likes it in my family, that the cover is the-- the family picture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But for all you bastards out there who dare to say anything about it, that it never happened-- there are such morons in this world.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look at them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were not phantom people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is my mother and my sisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how dare you say anything?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
